Package: sentimentcalculator
Type: Package
Title: A package for analyzing the true meaning of a text
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Isabelle", "Eliasson",
      email = "isabelle.eliasson@ki.se",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: This package will help you decide whether the sentiment of a text is positive, negative or neutral. 
    The package calculates a sentiment score by analyzing keywords, which helps determine the meaning of the text. 
    
    The functions have been designed to be run in the following order
    format_text() -> sentiment_counts() -> sentiment_results()
    
    This package uses the SnowballC package for word stemming.
  
